Package: swingeR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Selecting Low-Relatedness Breeding Groups and
        Screening VCF Data
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Jonathan Sandoval-Castillo Yuma248", email = "jonathan.sandoval-castillo@flinders.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides three sets of tools. (1) Given a pairwise kinship/relatedness
    data frame and per-individual sex and internal relatedness values, selects
    sets of non-overlapping breeding/family groups that satisfy user-specified
    relatedness thresholds, with an optional auto-tuning mode that relaxes
    thresholds when no valid solution exists. (2) Helper functions for
    summarizing SNP- and individual-level quality/heterozygosity metrics from
    VCF files (via 'vcfR') and for converting VCF files to GDS format (via
    'SNPRelate') for downstream population genetics analyses. (3) An
    interactive relatedness-network visualization built on 'visNetwork'.
